    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Photographic prints made by the diffusion transfer process from film packets that contain their own developing chemicals and are exposed in a special camera.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
